    <p>We provide a safe and secure checkout for payment. Our payments are processed through Stripe&reg. We also use 256 bit SSL encryption on our website. In order to provide a high degree of privacy, SSL encrypts data that is transmitted across the web. This means that anyone who tries to intercept any data will only see a garbled mix of characters that is impossible to decrypt.
      If you look above in your browsers address bar you will see a lock icon next to our website name which shows that our website is securely encrypted using 256 bit https protocol.
      So rest assured every payment made on our website is 100% safe and secure. We also allow bitcoin payments as well. 
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>

